original_title: TNA One Night Only: Joker's Wild 2
overview: 24 men compete in a tournament for $100,000. It was made up of tag team matches in which the partners were randomly drawn in a lottery and teams had to work together to advance to the main event Battle Royal, with the grand prize of US$100,000. It took place on February 2, 2014, from the National Indoor Arena in Birmingham, England and Aired on PPV on May 9, 2014.
title: TNA One Night Only: Joker's Wild 2
